                            <comment id="16692436" author="icleasby" created="Mon, 19 Nov 2018 23:43:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One line patch for:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/compare/cassandra-3.11...PenguinRage:Nodetool-cfstats-prints-out-index-names-twice-3.11&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;3.11&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

